Main Navigation (Bottom Tab Bar for Mobile):

Home/Dashboard: Overview, quick actions, recent alerts
Learn: Training modules, resources, expert articles
My Farm: Records, compliance, analytics
Alerts: Notifications, outbreak map, updates
More: Profile, settings, community, support

Dashboard Widgets (Customizable):

Current risk score with trend
Upcoming tasks and reminders
Recent alerts summary
Compliance status
Quick actions (Log activity, Start assessment, View training)
Farm performance metrics

7.4 Accessibility Features

Visual: High contrast mode, adjustable font sizes, screen reader support
Audio: Text-to-speech for all written content, audio descriptions for videos
Motor: Large touch targets (minimum 44x44 pixels), voice input, simplified gestures
Cognitive: Clear language, consistent navigation, step-by-step instructions, progress indicators
Literacy: Icon-based navigation, video tutorials, visual instructions, voice interface


